title: Borbaggretsuko
body:
Retsuko: Haida, I’m pregnant.

Haida: HOORAY!

Retsuko: I don’t wanna keep it, tho.

Haida: Aw, why not?

Retsuko: My career!

Haida: BABY KILLER!

Retsuko: *slap*

Haida: Ow. *leaves*

Retsuko: WAAAAAAAAAAAAA

*748 years later*

Haida: Hey, Retsy!

Retsuko: Fuck off.

Haida: TAKE ME BAAAAACK

Retsuko: No.

Haida: Pweeeeease?

Retsuko: No.

Fenneko: Hey. :3

Haida: WAT

Retsuko: My parents are Red Panddhists, and the abortion blew chunks, so Fenneko cheered me up. Now we fuck.

Haida: Naw, man, you gotta come back with me!

Retsuko: NO.

Fenneko: Hey, don’t be mean.

Haida: BEGONE THOT *pushes Fenneko to a table*

Fenneko: Ow. :3

Retsuko: YOU DED *throws Haida outside, into a dumpster that’s on fire, and he dies, press F to pay respects*

Fenneko: You okay?

Retsuko: Yeah. *and then they fuck*

TEH EDN

summary: LOLLL I HAD NO IDEA AGGRETSUKO-THEMED KARAOKE BARS EXISTED 😂😂😂 If you haven’t watched #aggretsuko yet, do yourself a favor and...
caption:
LOLLL I HAD NO IDEA AGGRETSUKO-THEMED KARAOKE BARS EXISTED 😂😂😂 If you haven’t watched #aggretsuko yet, do yourself a favor and watch it - it’s only 1 season and it’s on Netflix and it’s hilarious ahahahas
.
ALSO I was super surprised that I remembered the lyrics and rap to “Baby” by Justin Bieber 😂😂😂 I haven’t listened to that song in years ahahas but I think everyone sang it so often when it was all the hype that it’s just permanently ingrained in our minds xD
.
Happy birthday @stclu and thanks for inviting me to celebrate with you!!! It was so much fun losing my voice belting “Listen” and “Perfect” and all those other songs with you 😂 I’m so proud of you and excited for you ^-^
.
If you haven’t heard yet, @stclu and @alwaysalyssamarie started an AMAZING podcast called Tea Talk! Go check them out :D
.

summary: Japan Haul XD Here is most of my haul from Japan (not counting snacks). Lots of Mob Psycho 100 stuff (any dupes or non...
caption:
Japan Haul XD

Here is most of my haul from Japan (not counting snacks). Lots of Mob Psycho 100 stuff (any dupes or non Mob/Reigen/Ekubo are up for grabs).

Unfortunately Gangsta seems to belong forgotten as I hardly saw anything while browsing the recycled anime shops. Everything that I did pick up were pre-purchased before my trip and sent to some family living in country. Super stoked for the Bunch Comic mags as I took a chance on the two older ones hoping they’ll have the Fortunesta Tarot sheets included (they did!) and I was able to snag the issue w/ Ch 55 before catching my flight back home.

summary: Thought it be fun to see what characters are like me in terms of personality: fun, sarcastic, quite, perceptive, out going,...
body:
Thought it be fun to see what characters are like me in terms of personality: fun, sarcastic, quite, perceptive, out going, opinionate, child like, anxious a lot but try to pull though it, caring, polite, rational, cynical yet optimistic at times, smart/wise, recluse, mature, selfless.

This was fun and good way to understand yourself more I suggest you doing it sometime!
